descriptionHtml:
v2: Added alduin feet model. Renamed the original model \"Light Clawed feet\". Removed smithing requirements.
v1: Original.

Craftable pair of \"boots\".

Inspired by the Pharlan mod from Morrowind a while back, I tried to rig the feet from the hagraven model onto the CBBE female body. After much retopo work, remodeling, reskinning, texturing, I had a semi-acceptable result. Mostly intended as a modder\'s resource. I most likely won\'t work on this further until a real high heels mod comes out.

Will clip with armors that cover the lower legs. Not exactly avoidable with the model.

Completely free for use/editing/modding, but some credit would be appreciated. May be useful for modders wanting to do an anthro dragon race (really want one of those, thank you.)
author: jim
